songs.title: Your Mine*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

Said you got hearts in your Eyes
But I can tell that you been with a lot of other guys
Look me in face , you tell lies , you tell me lies

Niggas try to take my chain , they not tryna die
Niggas i be with, will leave you hospitalize
I don't go no where without my Glock and my 9
I dont do no percocets no more , i ain't tryna die

You dont even gotta worry girl, cause ur mine
Say i be in my bag , but i ain't even in my prime
[?] Melody, since
New FashionNova jeans...
